{
  "texts": [
    "In paper [17], they use RoBERTa as the main model.",
    "But at the same time, additional CRF layers were added, and training was performed on two tasks.",
    "The results show that this combination is better than just using RoBERTa.",
    "In the article [21], the author proposes the TD-BERT model, which is similar to the model in which a fully connected network is added to the BERT network for classification.",
    "The difference is that TD-BERT adds a maximum pooling layer after BERT, which allows the classifier to make better use of location information.The BERT model uses a lot of English corpora for training and has a very large English corpus."
  ]
}